** ERR
E-01 SELECTION INSTRUCTIONS ARE 1 AND 2.
E-02 ENTER THE WORK TAG NO.
E-03 NOT FOUND IN A-PICS2 FIXED ORDER-PLACEMENT CUMULATIVE FILE.
E-04 ENTER THE NUMBER OF BOXES.
E-05 DUPLICATE SCAN ERROR.
E-06 BAR CODE NOT ENTERED.
E-07 NOT FOUND IN PART INFORMATION M/F.
E-08 BAR CODE WAS NOT READ CORRECTLY -- PLEASE SCAN AGAIN.
E-09 DUPLICATE SCAN ERROR.
E-10 NOT FOUND IN INSTRUCTION KANBAN M/F.
E-11 SHOULD BE A MULTIPLE OF PRODUCITON LOT.
